talk on my radio Xiaomi walks quietly behind the man when he gets to the door

03:24.120 --> 03:38.040
she puts her hand on his arm please come with me she says could I go back to the

03:38.040 --> 03:57.320
screens and then I see her wow who's that girl what girl I can see lots of

