08:39.800 --> 08:55.800
hat and go over to her excuse me I say is this your little boy's hat she smiles at me oh thank you

08:55.800 --> 09:12.440
she says Greg look it's your hat Greg laughs she puts out her hand and takes the hat from me is

09:12.440 --> 09:29.400
she wearing a ring no there is no ring on her hand Wednesday is the best day of the week I think 10

09:29.400 --> 09:41.840
minutes later I am near the flowers when Leon speaks to me on my radio mark go to the door he

09:41.840 --> 09:58.440
says you must stop her the girl with red hair what what's happening I say go quickly now it's the

