little boy he's got one of the red planes those red planes children take them all the time because

10:12.120 --> 10:23.800
they like the color then they get to the door and the alarm rings children cry and their mothers get

10:23.880 --> 10:39.640
angry I hate those planes when I get to the door the alarm is ringing the girl with red hair is

10:39.640 --> 10:52.360
standing there and her face is red what's happening she says please come back into the store for a

10:52.360 --> 11:06.360
minute I say we go back into the store and the alarm stops this young man has got the answer I

11:06.440 --> 11:12.280
