14:11.020 --> 14:21.660
anybody can see that I don't want to look but I can't take my eyes away from the screen

14:22.460 --> 14:30.860
then they all go down the road away from the store I look around the room

14:30.860 --> 14:41.500
Leon and Charmy are in the store and the room is very quiet it feels cold

14:42.140 --> 14:56.700
