18:15.500 --> 18:25.260
the girl with red hair looks at me and smiles just a minute she says don't I know you

18:26.780 --> 18:31.100
she's talking to me why can't I say anything

18:33.100 --> 18:43.660
in the store I say at last in mason's store with your little boy and the red plane

18:45.100 --> 18:54.860
the girl with red hair laughs oh with Greg she says I remember

18:55.580 --> 19:10.380
but he isn't my baby he's clairs this is my sister Claire she's his mother the second girl with red hair waves at me

19:14.540 --> 19:23.100
but I always see you with him I say I look after Greg on Wednesday mornings

19:23.900 --> 19:30.300
and we always go to masons she says then I meet Claire

19:31.820 --> 19:43.260
well usually that is but not this week just then a good looking man in a black jacket arrives

19:43.580 --> 19:57.500
sorry I'm late he says and kisses Claire hi Kate Claire smiles at him and the girl with red hair says hello

19:58.860 --> 20:11.420
I'm starting to understand this is Claire's husband and Greg's father and the girl with red hair is called Kate

20:13.340 --> 20:29.980
my face is red hey I'm sorry I say to Kate it's well Greg's got your hair and your eyes

20:31.500 --> 20:41.740
but I can see now he's got clairs hair and eyes of course it's okay Kate says

20:42.540 --> 20:54.140
it happens all the time people say isn't your little boy happy and sometimes I just say yes he is

