Claire and her husband go off to dance and I get Kate a drink here you are Kate my name's Mark

21:09.020 --> 21:25.260
Mark thanks Mark she says so you work in masons yes I say I work in security I look for little boys with red

21:25.260 --> 21:37.020
planes and girls with red hair and do you find them I find lots of little boys with red planes

21:39.580 --> 21:53.500
